subject: Implement GUI
description:
## Feature Request
#### Description
Need to extend a Graphical User Interface (GUI) to the existing `Guet` command-line tool, so that the user experience is smooth.


#### Notes on todos

- [ ] - Add user-friendly layouts.
- [ ] - Add more themes
- [ ] - Make window persistent and resizable 
- [ ] - Customizeable themes
- [ ] - Grab commands from the under interface
- [ ] - Add 'User Preferences' section
